<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Return Policy - The Shirt Store</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f8fc;
      color: #333;
    }

    .center {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .pageheading h1 {
      font-size: 2.8em;
      color: #0056b3;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .policy {
      width: 80%;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .policy h2 {
      color: #d63384;
      font-size: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #ffc107;
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .policy p, .policy ul {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      line-height: 1.8em;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .policy ul {
      list-style: disc inside;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 1em;
      color: #6c757d;
    }

    .footer b {
      color: #17a2b8;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="center">
  <a href="${pageContext.request.contextPath}/">
    <img src="images/ShirtStoreLogo.png" class="img-fluid" alt="The Shirt Store Logo" style="width: 150px;"/>
  </a>
</div>

<div class="center pageheading">
  <h1>Return Policy</h1>
</div>

<div class="policy">
  <h2>Our Commitment to Your Satisfaction</h2>
  <p>We aim to ensure that you are completely satisfied with your purchase. If for any reason you are not, our return policy allows you to request a return or exchange subject to the terms outlined below.</p>

  <h2>1. Eligibility for Returns</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Items must be returned within <b>30 days</b> of delivery.</li>
    <li>Products must be in their original condition, unworn, unwashed, and with all tags and packaging intact.</li>
    <li>Sale or clearance items may not be eligible for returns unless explicitly stated.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Gift cards.</li>
    <li>Personalized or custom-made products.</li>
    <li>Items marked as "Final Sale."</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Return Process</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Log in to your account and visit the <b>Order History</b> page.</li>
    <li>Select the order and item(s) you wish to return and click "Request Return."</li>
    <li>Follow the provided instructions to generate a return label.</li>
    <li>Pack the item securely and include a copy of your receipt or order confirmation.</li>
    <li>Ship the package to the return address provided.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Please note that customers are responsible for return shipping costs unless the return is due to an error on our part (e.g., incorrect or defective items).</p>

  <h2>4. Refund Policy</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Refunds will be issued to the original payment method within <b>7-10 business days</b> after receiving and inspecting the returned item(s).</li>
    <li>Shipping charges are non-refundable unless the return is due to a mistake by The Shirt Store.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Exchange Policy</h2>
  <p>If you would like to exchange an item for a different size or color, please initiate a return and place a new order for the desired item. This ensures faster processing and availability.</p>

  <h2>6. Damaged or Defective Items</h2>
  <p>If you receive a damaged or defective item, please contact our customer service team immediately at <b>support@theshirtstore.com</b> or call us at <b>0123456789</b>. We will arrange for a replacement or refund at no additional cost to you.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>For questions or assistance regarding returns, please contact us:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b>Email:</b> support@theshirtstore.com</li>
    <li><b>Phone:</b> 0123456789</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="footer">
  <p><b>Copyright &copy; 2024 by The Shirt Store. All rights reserved.</b></p>
</div>
</body>
</html>